ActFarm Income Protection Act
SubjectContributions to assist poultry producers in Alberta
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to provide for FEDERAL CONTRIBUTIONS OF UP TO $1,200,000 TO ASSIST POULTRY PRODUCERS in ALBERTA whose flocks were destroyed following an outbreak of SALMONELLA ENTERIDITIS.
